- I Will Always Love You: The Best Of Whitney Houston is categorized as Pop; Vocal Pop — that category implies a vocal‑forward collection of hit singles with radio‑friendly arrangements and strong, memorable choruses. Those are the exact production/arrangement qualities I value (clear lead vocals and concise, sing‑along choruses that make a greatest‑hits disc easy to play repeatedly). While some Whitney ballads are powerful and dramatic, the core alignment with vocal prominence and pop single production fits my stated preferences far better than the problems listed for the other option.
